Nge2
{ 6.Nf3  is much less frequent. Black has a good game with natural moves like  6...Bd6  7.O-O  O-O  8.Re1  Nc6= }
6... Bd6 7. O-O O-O 8. d4 c6
{ Restricts White's light-squared bishop and takes firm control over the d5 square. Coming next are ...Bf5 and ...Nd7 with an excellent game. }
