Nge2 { heading to g3. } 5... e6 6. Ng3 Be7 7. Qe2
{ There's no rush in castling kingside and potentially walking into an attack with h4-h5. Even though this attack is objectively dubious, it gives White chances to murky the waters, which I'd rather avoid. Instead, I prefer developing the queenside first with }
