{ is both novel and strong, improving over the game ½-½ @@StartBracket@@40@@EndBracket@@ Rowson,J @@StartBracket@@2569@@EndBracket@@-Kramnik,V @@StartBracket@@2793@@EndBracket@@ London 2013. Black clears the way for ...e5 with an excellent game. }
