{ was Negi's suggestion in the book GM Repertoire: 1. e4 vs Minor Defences. }
20... O-O 21. O-O
{ 21.Nd7?  loses material to  21...Qxd4  stepping out of the fork with a counterattack on the a1 rook.  22.Qe5  Qa7  23.Nxf8  Bf6−+  is decisive. }
