12... c5
{ is novel and improves over the game ½-½ @@StartBracket@@81@@EndBracket@@ Naiditsch,A @@StartBracket@@2673@@EndBracket@@-Van Wely,L  @@StartBracket@@2653@@EndBracket@@ Jurmala 2016, where Black played the inferior 12...Bc6. Striking in the center is far more powerful. }
13. d5 exd5 14. Nxd5 Nxd5 15. Bxd5 Nc6
{ Black looks quite fine to me with ...Nb4 and ...Rd8 on the agenda. } *

