{ White has just blocked with f2-f3. Where should the bishop retreat to? } 6...
Bd7
{ This is the correct square for the bishop, where it's not exposed to tempo gaining moves like g2-g4.   And not  6...Bf5?  due to  7.g4!  Bg6  8.f4±  f5 is coming and Black's in trouble. }
