12. Be2
{ White has just retreated the light-squared bishop to safety. Find Black's best move. }
12... Ba3
{ Hello! This is one of my favorite tactical shots in the Scandinavian. Black undermines the b2 pawn, which is the sole defender of White's knight. }
13. Rb1
{ 13.Bc1  is White's best defense. Following  13...Bb4  14.O-O  Rhe8=+  Black has the upper hand. White's minor pieces are passive and uncoordinated. }
13... Bxb2 14. Rxb2 Qxc3+ { is lights out. } *

