12... gxf6 13. Bxe6 { Black is doing very well after } 13... Qxe6+ 14. Qe2 Nc6
15. Rd1 Rg8
{ The g2 pawn is hanging and ...Rg4-e4 is also coming. Black has no problems whatsoever. }
