12. Bb2
{ White has dropped his bishop to b2 and is ready to retreat the other one to a2, clearing the way for c2-c4 to expand on the queenside. How can we prevent White from achieving this and rolling us over on the queenside? }
12... a5
{ puts immediate pressure on the b4 pawn, neutralizing White's ambitious plan. }
