{ This chapter contains over 100 tactical puzzles all taken from games in the Scandinavian defense. They were selected to familiarize you with a wide range of tactical resources in this defense.  Most of these tactical patterns have occurred in multiple games, that is they are typical motifs. A small minority were included solely based on their aesthetic value  (after all, having fun should not be underestimated in the journey towards mastery!)  .    It's Black to move and win in all the puzzles. As one of the beta testers likes to say: @@StartBlockQuote@@You can run but you can't escape #TeamScandi!@@EndBlockQuote@@Have fun taking down White in all these puzzles!  PS: if you come across any cool tactical themes in your own games or other Scandinavian games, just leave a comment in the Comments & Notes box below and I'll be happy to add them to this chapter. }
